  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>This pattern is designed to evaluate different pattern networks based on an index that can be read from various nodes.</p><hr/><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"PxrSwitch-Switch\">Switch</h3><h4 id=\"PxrSwitch-Index\">Index</h4><p>This float value indicates what part of the network to evaluate and is often read from an attribute. Values are read as:</p><p>-0.5 to 0.49 are input 0</p><p>  0.5 to 1.49 are input 1</p><p>  1.5 to 2.49 are input 2, so on and so forth.</p><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"PxrSwitch-Inputs\">Inputs</h3><h4 id=\"PxrSwitch-InputsRGB\">Inputs RGB</h4><p>An array of inputs to be evaluated based on the returned index value.</p><p><br/></p><p>Below is a simple example where each sphere transform is assigned a user attribute as the index, 0.0, 1.0, 2.0. The available colors and their index are Red[0], Green[1], and Blue[2] (three inputs added to the Inputs RGB array)</p><p>The same <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542213836/PxrSurface\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542213836\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrSurface</a> is attached to the three spheres and a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542222552/PxrAttribute\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222552\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrAttribute</a> node is connected to the Diffuse Color input of the material.</p><p>The attribute can be whatever name you desire with a Float data type.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224974/rps_pxrSwitchExample.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330622358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224974/rps_pxrSwitchExample.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330622358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224990\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rps_pxrSwitchExample.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224974\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b3b292ba-feef-4a6d-9fd7-d12ec20e6d1f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224974/rps_pxrSwitchExample.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330622358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=888&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224974/rps_pxrSwitchExample.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330622358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=250 1x\"></span></p>"
    }
